title: UFYB 5: How to Survive Family Time
itunes:title: How to Survive Family Time
description:
Today, we’re talking about how to survive family time during the stressful holiday season. Join me on this episode as I share a powerful strategy to help you prepare for family time, skip the drama, and actually enjoy your holidays.

Get full show notes and more information here: http://bit.ly/2iCTrUa
